{"tid":2510406,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"灣仔單位涉藏逾百支汽油彈案 理大女生判監3年2個月","createTime":"2021-04-30T06:47:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T06:56:29.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d24556d6748e5b8af7bbe00c9530e949c7412eb1","tid":2510406,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T06:47:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15372\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F15372&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnT85RZDHrhPshgzcG8Nqr5vw%3D&h=98bf92ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15372</a><br />\n<br />\n#區域法院第廿八庭<br />\n#葉佐文法官 #判刑<br />\n👤楊(22) #1102灣仔<br />\n🛑已還押逾17個月🛑<br />\n<br />\n控罪2：管有物品意圖摧毀或損毀財產<br />\n被告人被控於2019年11月2日，於灣仔堅拿道西10號冠景樓4樓F室，保管或控制59瓶汽油彈和79瓶半製成汽油彈，意圖使用以摧毀或損毀他人財產。<br />\n<br />\n簡單背景：<br />\n被告人於2021年4月20日在葉佐文法官席前承認控罪1的交替控罪，即「管有物品意圖摧毀或損毀財產」。同日葉佐文法官決定把被告人的判刑程序押後至2021年4月30日進行。<br />\n=================<br />\n上次的聆訊的內容(感謝臨直🙏🏻)：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15104\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F15104&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnT85RZDHrhPshgzcG8Nqr5vw%3D&h=68f4dc37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15104</a><br />\n==================<br />\n辯方律師代表：#郭憬憲大律師<br />\n控方律師代表：#張卓勤高級檢控官<br />\n<br />\n🛑法庭決定以4年9個月監禁作為量刑起點，因被告人及早認罪可獲1/3刑罰扣減，此外沒有其他減刑因素，故總刑期為3年2個月監禁🛑"},{"pid":"ecf7c6f5b78fdb1c99eb289e11908e3a75c72407","tid":2510406,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T06:48:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23d8e1f4c0ed0a0f3e82013b61a4a6334064ecc3","tid":2510406,"uid":362346,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T06:48:22.000Z","msg":"22歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ad7570fd2eb7ed031ec78944bab85adecfec26b","tid":2510406,"